{"tid":1269533,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日我22歲生日，想提早講個願望","createTime":"2019-06-30T15:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T15:31:43.000Z","uid":90589,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e9b556fb06791c6a94b0ae25c010c80fabdcd19e","tid":1269533,"uid":90589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:05:13.000Z","msg":"我今年大學畢業，未有工返，6月發生咁多事<br />\n於是就同大家發左一個月夢<br />\n我曾經都係個政治冷感既人<br />\n今次積極既程度令我同屋企人都炒曬大獲<br />\n我由最初滿腔熱血，見到咁撚多人反對<br />\n心諗仲唔成功？政府仲正面回應民意？<br />\n到後來見到高官既嘴臉、藍屍既誣衊、烈士既離世<br />\n我真係成日睇新聞都會嬲到想爆血管<br />\n<br />\n攰<br />\n真係身心都攰<br />\n我知好多同路人都係咁<br />\n大家見自己既行動都咁樣<br />\n依然改變唔到現實<br />\n自然會覺得絕望，覺得以死相迫可以警惕社會<br />\n但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">夠啦！</span></span><br />\n唔係話烈士犧牲唔值得<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">太值得啦！</span></span><br />\n我地仲係到班人先唔值得有同伴犧牲<br />\n<br />\n無論今次結果係點<br />\n都唔代表我地無做到野<br />\n可能結果未必係我地想要既<br />\n但唔代表我地無影響到某啲野<br />\n唔代表我地無改變到任何野<br />\n至少我地知道一個社會接近1/3人都係好同伴！<br />\n所以絕對唔孤單<br />\n亦無想像中咁絕望<br />\n<br />\n所以大家！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再死</span></span><br />\n呢個係我生日願望<br />\n我希望我地呢1/3人可以繼續係呢個社會抗爭落去<br />\n見證大家既所有行動"},{"pid":"cd356aad10f3cb9eaa8d8f19815343a2e681bc17","tid":1269533,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4852cf7e10218bd4c10a8fba2c6206bff2555f41","tid":1269533,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"與您同在"},{"pid":"f1d4f707f30b110d6b0dfac1e60613611ddca7e3","tid":1269533,"uid":225144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<br />\n但真係好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16be11b168574e76ebb95b66ee2dab64565a097d","tid":1269533,"uid":11049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:09:44.000Z","msg":"預祝你生日快樂，大家繼續一齊努力"},{"pid":"6c00dd34684458f54eb165e2be9f31464387d05d","tid":1269533,"uid":225144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:09:55.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一開吹水區，已經見到無數既post都係關於想尋死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n各位巴絲真係唔好諗咁多呀，我同大家一樣都好失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n如果你地真係好頂唔順既，不如入來呢個tg gp，我<br />\n地一齊面對啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/KVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=3541ec5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/KVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg</a>"},{"pid":"abaab40bfcbfd8b0dc5df76b038f1d63c9eddbad","tid":1269533,"uid":90589,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHknBH6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHknBH6.png&h=0ae3d729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽聞壽星仔係大曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望我既生日願望可以成真<br />\nbtw聽日街上見"},{"pid":"ee6a373789b81fda9de2402d10f6d903a510fa79","tid":1269533,"uid":65409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abaab40bfcbfd8b0dc5df76b038f1d63c9eddbad","tid":1269533,"uid":90589,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":